description: 2 newcomers face off with the help of veterans Lyla and Wynona. Wynona is tough and scrappy and she is teaching her teammate Sahara to be the same way- they make a bad-ass duo. It's a very close first round with the lovely Lyla showing Andre Shakti how to be cute and ruthless at the same time.
title: Tagteam with fresh meat! Wynona throws down and schools some bitches!
